1) Algoritham for a adition of two number.

Step-1 : start
Step-2 : get input 1 and input 2 
Step-3 : sum of given value 1 and value 2
Step-4 : print sum of value 1 and value 2
Step-5 : end 


2) Algoritham for a area of circle.

