Step-5 : end 

3) Algoritham for a adition of a all even numbers.

Step-1 : start
Step-2 : read limited number of n
Step-3 : assign the value of i where i=1
Step-4 : assign i=n 
Step-5 : if i is not equal to n then i%2
Step-6 : if i%2==0 then print the number of sum 
Step-7 : end
